{"tid":1199820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，最後一次","createTime":"2019-06-10T15:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T15:15:51.000Z","uid":98283,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"29a19b26d9f9a3c22383a48a8577c07f2409a693","tid":1199820,"uid":98283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:00:39.000Z","msg":"身為一個00後，係69個日，警察係海富第一次用胡椒噴霧個時，我目睹左成個過程。從一堆人衝出馬路，搬鐵馬，樓梯既人叫佢地返來，警察衝過來，救人，全部野都係一瞬間發生。我第一次遊行，見到香港人手無寸鐵，捨身擋車，為既就係向政府，警察提出自己既訴求。但係喺樓梯上面既人就個個都作壁上觀，得把口叫人返來話危險，冇人諗過佢地咁樣衝係為乜。件事去到一半，我記得有位女士除低個口罩，向上對啲花生友講「我地咁辛苦，為咩呀。」樓梯突然靜左落來，冇人答到。<br />\n<br />\n見住成年人冷眼旁觀，我終於見到香港人既自私，個個得把口勁，屌人老母就最撚叻，要行動就個個不了。話要靠和理非解決問題，結果係乜？612你地唔衝，咁就唯有用我地呢班後生既未來去撘救你地既自私。<br />\n<br />\n最後一次，一齊衝定我自己衝。"},{"pid":"36b823715d0bcc4905d082fcf92c54ad38134388","tid":1199820,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:01:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff13ca3a0913930966ff19f5f8dcf08924d7c8a","tid":1199820,"uid":98283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:07:45.000Z","msg":"香港人，訓撚醒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e6af2b912c26d1bc4ed315fc4c88f3067823a9","tid":1199820,"uid":97603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wn8tPxu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwn8tPxu.png&h=19956a57&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wtFgdZb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwtFgdZb.png&h=d6c3eade&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86e5aa289b69d25b2bd35836fe642eeeda1fb94f","tid":1199820,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:15:26.000Z","msg":"勇武！"},{"pid":"9df53ccc42f427ffd091310976ae00661f791169","tid":1199820,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:15:51.000Z","msg":"衝！"}]}